		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The soldering may not be pretty, but it definitely gets the job done.
<br />
<br />I can't see any other way to fit all that stuff in a tiny Famicom cart. Good job!
<br />
<br />I'm going to be soldering an EPROM on the underside of a FF3 cart to make my dual-language reproduction.
<br />
<br />I got really lucky and found a nice tiny SPDT slider switch that fits PERFECTLY in the hole at the top corners of famicom carts.

		

